== Changelog ==
= 1.3.8 =
* Cleaned up featured slider query code
* Added valign styles for tables
* Added caption on attachment page

= 1.3.7 =
* Added small tag styling
* Removed month limit on Sitemap template
* Removed stats code option

= 1.3.6 =
* Added Google+ icon
* Fixed display of excerpt on archive/category pages

= 1.3.5 =
* Fixed font size for TextWidgets

= 1.3.4 =
* Fixed bug with featured slider flickering in certain situations
* Fixed text widget spacing
* Added dl and table styling
* Fixed image stretching in old versions of Internet Explorer

= 1.3.3 =
* Fixing a few bugs with the attachment template

= 1.3.2 =
* Improve line-height and font-size for sidebar text widgets

= 1.3.1 =
* Styled paragraph margins on featured slider to better fit the slider area

= 1.3 =
* Added option to include sticky posts in standard list (in addition to featured slider)
* Added support for the_excerpt on posts
* Added graceful slider degradation when Javascript disabled
* Slider can now contain 1 post (previously required at least 2)
* Added attachment template file for post attachment display
* Added support for static front pages with separate post pages - slider now appears on both

= 1.2.4 =
* Fixed max-width on pages without sidebars

= 1.2.3 =
* Fixed max-width on pages with sidebars

= 1.2.2 =
* Fixed images being squished on the full-width page template

= 1.2.1 =
* Fixed formatting bug on comments header

= 1.2.0 =
* Added CSS selectors for footer widgets
* Fixed front page to display proper number of "non-featured" posts when slider is enabled
* Fixed various translation bugs
* Removed duplicate header on custom search widget
* Changed admin styles to match WordPress defaults
* Made header clickable in featured slider
* Accessibility improvements on search form
* Fixed maximum widths for images & other media
* Fixed buggy "comments disabled/off" messages on posts with comments disabled

= 1.1.1 =
* Fixed SQL error when Featured Slider enabled with no sticky posts and a static front page.

= 1.1 =
* Replaced the old logo uploader with a faster version that uses WP core
* Strip tags from text in the featured slider to prevent breakage
* Hide featured slider unless 2 sticky posts are present
* Upgrade to the latest version of Slides (1.0.2)